  "prompt": "If I delete my Tinder account and uninstall the app, does my profile still show to those I've matched with?",
  "response": "If you delete your Tinder account, your profile should no longer be visible to anyone, including those you have matched with. Deleting your account removes your profile and all associated data from Tinder\u2019s servers. Therefore, your matches will not see your profile in their list of matches, and your conversations will disappear from their chat history.\n\nSimply uninstalling the app, however, does not delete your account. If you only uninstall the app without deleting your account, your profile may still be visible to others. To completely remove your presence on Tinder, you need to delete your account through the app before uninstalling it.",
